data.description: Discover your oasis of tranquility with this modern, two-bedroom bungalow, perfectly situated near breathtaking Canyon Lake and a short drive to Downtown New Braunfels. Ideal as your primary home or make this your get-away from the city. This haven is where contemporary design meets the beauty of Texas Hill Country. Built in 2018, this single-story gem is a blend of minimalism and harmony with nature. Its metal roof and exterior aesthetics are thoughtfully integrated into the serene landscape.    The spacious expansive .73-acre cul-de-sac lot offers ample space for relaxation and outdoor activities with no HOA or city taxes. This home is your gateway to a life of serene living amidst the picturesque Texas Hill Country.    The home includes a built-in storage closet, RV hookup, and fenced space for your pet. A 16x12 outbuilding offers electricity, water, lighting, and climate control—perfect for a workshop or office.
